<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:17:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国恒大前首席执行官以近一半的价格出售香港房屋</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-evergrandes-ex-ceo-sells-hong-kong-home-almost-half-purchase-price-2024-06-14/</link><description>据一位房地产经纪人称，中国监管机构最近称其“无法联系”的中国恒大前首席执行官已出售其在香港的房屋，购买价损失 7,400 万港元（合 948 万美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 06:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-evergrandes-ex-ceo-sells-hong-kong-home-almost-half-purchase-price-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲女子冠军联赛将于 8 月启动，一等奖奖金为 130 万美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-womens-champions-league-launch-august-with-13m-first-prize-2024-06-14/</link><description>亚洲足球联合会周五表示，首届亚洲女子冠军联赛将于 8 月拉开帷幕，22 支球队将争夺 130 万美元的最高奖金，这是亚洲女子俱乐部足球的最高奖金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 05:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/asian-womens-champions-league-launch-august-with-13m-first-prize-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰峰会吸引了世界领导人，但未能孤立俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-summit-attracts-world-leaders-fails-isolate-russia-2024-06-14/</link><description>世界领导人将在本周末与乌克兰总统泽伦斯基一起参加峰会，探讨结束欧洲自第二次世界大战以来最致命冲突的方法，但俄罗斯没有受到邀请，这次活动将达不到基辅孤立莫斯科的目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 05:10:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-summit-attracts-world-leaders-fails-isolate-russia-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>Rystad Energy 首席执行官表示，得益于可再生能源，日本到 2060 年将实现能源独立</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/japan-could-be-energy-independent-by-2060-thanks-renewables-rystad-energy-ceo-2024-06-14/</link><description>Rystad Energy 咨询公司首席执行官 Jarand Rystad 表示，由于太阳能、风能以及蓄电池的扩张，日本作为煤炭和液化天然气 (LNG) 的主要买家，到 2060 年可能实现能源独立。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 05:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/japan-could-be-energy-independent-by-2060-thanks-renewables-rystad-energy-ceo-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰峰会：谁将出席在瑞士举行的会谈？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/who-will-attend-who-will-skip-switzerlands-ukraine-summit-2024-06-14/</link><description>大约 90 个国家和组织已确认参加 6 月 15 日至 16 日在瑞士举行的峰会，旨在为乌克兰的和平开辟一条道路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 05:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/who-will-attend-who-will-skip-switzerlands-ukraine-summit-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>支持者称中国#MeToo活动人士被判五年监禁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-metoo-activist-sentenced-five-years-prison-supporters-say-2024-06-14/</link><description>支持者告诉路透社，中国一家法院周五以颠覆罪判处 #MeToo 活动领袖黄学勤五年监禁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-metoo-activist-sentenced-five-years-prison-supporters-say-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>支持者称，中国#MeToo活动人士黄因颠覆罪被判五年徒刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-metoo-activist-huang-expected-be-sentenced-subversion-friday-supporters-2024-06-14/</link><description>据一个争取释放黄雪琴的组织和法庭判决书副本称，中国南方#MeToo运动领袖黄雪琴周五在中国南方一家法院被判犯有颠覆国家罪，被判处五年徒刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-metoo-activist-huang-expected-be-sentenced-subversion-friday-supporters-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行谨慎立场后日本股市上涨，日元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-14/</link><description>日本股市上涨，跑赢较疲软的亚洲市场，而在日本央行表示将在未来开始削减巨额债券购买规模后，日元普遍下跌，打破了一些关于日本央行将更早开始这一进程的押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 02:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>日本央行立场温和后日元下跌；欧元疲软走向每周损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-guard-ahead-boj-euro-stutters-with-weekly-loss-sight-2024-06-14/</link><description>日本央行(BOJ)维持利率不变并表示未来将削减债券购买，日元周五跌至一个多月低点，而深陷政治动荡的欧元将每周下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 01:32:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-guard-ahead-boj-euro-stutters-with-weekly-loss-sight-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理李克强在贸易促进中会见新西兰商界领袖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-premier-li-meet-new-zealand-business-leaders-amid-trade-boost-2024-06-14/</link><description>中国总理李强周五会见了新西兰政府和商界领袖，这是他对邻国澳大利亚进行区域访问的第二天，这标志着太平洋国家与其最大贸易伙伴之间关系的升温。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 01:18:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-premier-li-meet-new-zealand-business-leaders-amid-trade-boost-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业寻求对欧盟进口猪肉进行反倾销调查，加剧紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-firms-apply-anti-dumping-probe-eu-pork-imports-global-times-says-2024-06-14/</link><description>据官方支持的《环球时报》报道，中国企业已正式申请对从欧盟进口的猪肉进行反倾销调查，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收反补贴税后，紧张局势升级。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 01:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-firms-apply-anti-dumping-probe-eu-pork-imports-global-times-says-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国将主导七国集团最后一天，教皇将主导人工智能讨论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-dominate-final-day-g7-pope-lead-ai-discussions-2024-06-14/</link><description>七国集团 (G7) 领导人将于周五在年度峰会上举行最后一天的会谈，中国是首要议题，随后教皇方济各历史性地露面讨论人工智能 (AI)。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 00:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-dominate-final-day-g7-pope-lead-ai-discussions-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大公民承认窃取特斯拉商业机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/canadian-national-pleads-guilty-stealing-tesla-trade-secrets-2024-06-13/</link><description>据美国司法部（DOJ）称，一名中国加拿大居民周四在纽约联邦法院承认窃取特斯拉电动汽车电池制造商业机密并密谋将其出售给便衣政府特工。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/canadian-national-pleads-guilty-stealing-tesla-trade-secrets-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>党魁称，故意帮助其他国家的加拿大议员必须被撤职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-lawmakers-who-knowingly-helped-other-nations-must-be-removed-party-leader-2024-06-13/</link><description>加拿大一个政党的领导人周四表示，一份关于一些议会成员充当其他国家代理人的情报报告令人担忧，必须将冒犯的议员撤职。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-lawmakers-who-knowingly-helped-other-nations-must-be-removed-party-leader-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储持谨慎态度，但日本央行呢？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-13/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 21:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>